<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>أَعْمَى<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">اُنْظُرْ:</span> عَمًى.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أَعْوَانٌ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">اُنْظُرْ:</span> إِعَانَةٌ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>أَعْوَرُ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">انْظُرْ:</span> عَوَرٌ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>أَعْيَانٌ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">التَّعْرِيفُ:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>١ -<span class="c5"> الأَْعْيَانُ فِي اللُّغَةِ:</span> جَمْعُ عَيْنٍ،<span class="c5"> وَالْعَيْنُ لَهَا إِطْلاَقَاتٌ عَدِيدَةٌ مِنْهَا:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>الْعَيْنُ بِمَعْنَى الْمَال الْحَاضِرِ النَّاضِّ.<span class="c5"> يُقَال:</span> اشْتَرَيْتُ بِالدَّيْنِ <span class="c2">(أَيْ فِي الذِّمَّةِ)</span> أَوْ بِالْعَيْنِ أَيِ الْمَنْقُودِ الْحَاضِرِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَعَيْنُ الشَّيْءِ نَفْسُهُ، يُقَال أَخَذْتُ مَالِي بِعَيْنِهِ، أَيْ نَفْسَ مَالِي.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَالْعَيْنُ مَا ضُرِبَ مِنَ الدَّنَانِيرِ وَالدَّرَاهِمِ <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) لسان العرب المحيط مادة (عين) ، والمغرب، والزاهر، والمصباح المنير، والتعريفات للجرجاني.</p> </div>